{
    "Description" : {
        "Id" : "event_co_salesGus1",
        "Name" : "Travelling Salesman",
        "Details" : "You find yourself on the bridge, responding to a hail from a familiar vessel. Darius already in talks with a rather burly bearded man on the viewscreen.\r\n\r\nDarius calmly states, \"Commander, do you remember the Buccaneer that was fighting with the Pirates a while back? Well, its captain wanted to express his thanks.\"\r\n\r\nDarius continues, \"It appears that [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreGus],Gus Flanagan]], the swashbuckling captain of the Buccaneer, was able to bluff the Pirates into abandoning their attack. They hastily fled rather than contend with his favourite customers coming to his rescue.\"\r\n\r\nYang chuckles, \"And that would be us...I'm really starting to like this guy.\" \r\n\r\nGus goes into full salesman mode, \"Well if you are interested in some wares, I got the best prices hands down. Sadly, I'm always on the go and I can only move so much stuff around at one time so for 400 000 C-Bills you can choose a large crate of cargo from one of my three bays. <b>Bay One</b> is an assortment of mostly energy and support weapons. <b>Bay Two</b> has a mix of missiles and ballistics and <b>Bay Three</b> is mostly a hodge-podge of equipment and salvage.\"\r\n\r\nDarius folds his arms, \"Sounds like we're contestants in an old game show?\"\r\n\r\nGus smiles, \"I have over 2000 tonnes of cargo here. Now if you don't want any of it, then I'll gladly take my leave, no skin off my back...\"\r\n\r\n\"Now, now, we didn't say that!\", Darius backpedals and he turns to you, \"Well, Commander?\"",
        "Icon" : "uixTxrSpot_GusBucc"
    },
